file: ReduceResult.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Reducer\\ReduceResult"
type: readonly final class
summary: "ReduceResult is a readonly value object that encapsulates the outcome of a reducer operation, bundling the resulting RunState and a list of side-effect instructions. It serves as a pure data container to separate computation results from their execution, ensuring immutability and clear intent in the application's event processing flow."
